dcterms:description: This dataset includes vector graphics for floorplans. It contains 1,000 images with a total of 28,065 objects in 16 categories, such as armchair, tables, and windows. The images are evenly divided into 10 layouts, with half used for training and the other half for validation and testing.
dcterms:title: Floorplans

dcterms:description: This dataset includes vector graphics for diagrams. It contains 1,000 images with a total of 14,100 objects in 21 categories, such as diode and resistor. The dataset is split into training, validation, and test sets, ensuring that objects from the same category are included in both training and testing sets.
dcterms:title: Diagrams

dcterms:description: SESYD is a public database containing different types of vector graphic documents, with corresponding object detection ground truth, produced using the 3gT system.
dcterms:title: SESYD
